= Internal security

- @create_secret_service
- @expand_secret_service
- @create_hounds: Establish Redanian Hounds, militarised branch of Special Service
- @expand_hounds: Expand Redanian Hounds
- @dijkstra: Back

@create_secret_service
title: Establish Special Service
new-page: true
view-if: sec_ss_level = 0
choose-if: admin_cap >= sec_ss_establishcost
subtitle: Requires [+ sec_ss_establishcost +] bureaucratic effort
unavailable-subtitle: We need better bureaucracy!
on-arrival: {!
    Q.sec.ss.level = 1
    Q.sec_ss_level = 1
!}

- @security: Back

@expand_secret_service
title: Expand Special Service
new-page: true
view-if: sec_ss_level >= 1
choose-if: admin_cap >= sec_ss_expand
subtitle: Requires [+ sec_ss_expand +] bureaucratic effort
unavailable-subtitle: We need better bureaucracy!
on-arrival: {!
    Q.sec.ss.level += 1
    Q.sec_ss_level += 1
!}

- @security: Back

